W3C Specification

   The specification describes a CSS box model optimized for user
   interface design.
     * [http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-flexbox/]CSS Flexible Box Layout Module
       Level 1

Newsletter

     * [http://csslayout.news/]CSS Layout News
     * [http://css-weekly.com/]CSS Weekly
     * [http://responsivedesignweekly.com/]Responsive Design Weekly
     * [https://web-design-weekly.com/]Web Design Weekly

Books

     * [http://rachelandrew.co.uk/books/css3-layout-modules]CSS3 Layout
       Modules 2nd Edition - Rachel Andrew

