Libraries and Frameworks

   A list of incredible libraries based on flexbox.
     * [https://github.com/bem-incubator/bem-grid]Bem grid
     * [https://github.com/kristoferjoseph/flexboxgrid]Flexboxgrid
     * [https://afonsopacifer.github.io/flex-grid-framework/]Flex Grid
       Framework
     * [http://stylusgrid.com/]Flexbox Grid for Stylus
     * [https://github.com/henriquecustodia/fuux]Fuux - Fuux is a Flexbox
       library that uses the same flexbox interface like classes.
     * [https://github.com/erwstout/ginger/]Ginger Grid - A Flexbox grid
       framework named after a cute dog.
     * [http://bulma.io/]Bulma - A modern CSS framework based on Flexbox
     * [http://milligram.github.io/]Milligram - A minimalist CSS framework
     * [http://kaisermann.github.io/rolleiflex/]RolleiFLEX - Just a
       responsive flexbox grid
     * [https://lucasgruwez.github.io/waffle-grid]Waffle Grid - An easy to
       use flexbox grid system

Featured Projects

   Awesome projects about flexbox.
     * [http://codepen.io/collection/KegmA/]Cool examples of flexbox
       layout - A codepen a collection.
     * [https://github.com/potch/flex-box]flex-box - A Custom Element to
       make the basics of flexbox easier to use.
     * [https://github.com/philipwalton/flexbugs]Flexbugs - A
       community-curated list of flexbox issues and cross-browser
       workarounds for them.
     * [http://flexboxfroggy.com/]Flexbox Froggy - A game for learning CSS
       flexbox.
     * [http://www.flexboxpatterns.com/]Flexbox Patterns - Examples and
       source code that will teach you how to build UI components with CSS
       flexbox! What's flexbox?
     * [http://www.flexboxdefense.com/]Flexbox Defense - Tower Defense
       with a twist: all towers must be positioned with CSS Flexbox.
     * [http://madebymike.com.au/demos/flexbox-tester/]Flexbox tester -
       Understand how to calculate the width of flex items.
     * [https://github.com/google/flexbox-layout]Flexbox layout -
       FlexboxLayout is a library project which brings the similar
       capabilities of CSS Flexible Box Layout Module to Android.
     * [https://github.com/lucdion/FlexLayout]FlexLayout for iOS -
       FlexLayout brings flexbox to iOS using Swift. Concise, intuitive &
       chainable syntax.
     * [https://github.com/jxnblk/grid-styled]grid-styled - Flexbox based
       responsive ReactJS grid system built with styled-components
     * [https://www.webcomponents.org/element/PolymerElements/iron-flex-la
       yout]iron-flex-layout - Style mixins for cross-platform flex-box
       layouts
     * [https://github.com/afonsopacifer/post-apocalypse-flexbox]Post
       Apocalypse Flexbox
     * [https://github.com/tcoopman/react-flexbox]React-flexbox -
       Implementation of css flexbox in react with inline styles.
     * [https://github.com/jxnblk/reflexbox]Reflexbox - Responsive React
       flexbox grid system higher order component.
     * [https://github.com/philipwalton/solved-by-flexbox]Solved by
       flexbox - A showcase of problems once hard or impossible to solve
       with CSS alone, now made trivially easy with Flexbox.
     * [http://codepen.io/paultrone/pen/xwxNmQ?utm_campaign=CSS%2BLayout%2
       BNews&utm_medium=email&utm_source=CSS_Layout_News_6]Visualizing
       Flexbox - A neat little CodePen Demo to play around with Flex
       properties.
     * [https://css-flexbox.zeef.com/afonso.pacifer]ZEEF CSS Flexbox - The
       awesome flexbox on zeef.
     * [http://flexboxzombies.com/p/flexbox-zombies]Flexbox Zombies - A
       game for learning CSS flexbox.

